Remember (2015 film)
Remember is an upcoming American drama film directed by Atom Egoyan and written by Benjamin August. The film stars Dean Norris, Christopher Plummer, Martin Landau, Bruno Ganz, Heinz Lieven, JÃ¼rgen Prochnow, Gunter Lamprecht, Henry Czerny and Kim Roberts.
Production.
On April 30, 2014, it was announced that the film would be directed by Atom Egoyan, and would star Christopher Plummer, Martin Landau, Dean Norris, Bruno Ganz, Heinz Lieven and Gunter Lamprecht. Principal photography began on July 14, 2014.
